---
title: Dark Chocolate Mousse Pots with Almond Crumb
description: Rich, decadent and super simple to make, these dark chocolate mousse pots are seriously indulgent. Leave them with enough
time to set in the fridge, then top them with a super crunchy almond crumb and watch how quickly they'll become your favourite
sweet treat.
